hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.exec

Class ValueWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.exec.ValueWrapper

  • public class ValueWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper for a single value that can be either Integer or Double.

    Basic arithmetic operations are offered over that value. Numbers can also be given as Strings and null reference is treated as Integer with value 0. Other types will cause an exception.

    Author:
    Dan
